  "title": "Chiropractor",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an chiropractor who:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>is committed to reaching their full potential as a leader</li>\n  <li>has a strong desire to help people through spinal manipulative adjustments</li>\n  <li>is an effective team player</li>\n  <li>strongly believes in subluxation-based care</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We offer a tremendous amount of coaching, mentorship and practice-skills development, with an opportunity to lead your own team and have equity in the business in the future. Learn proven practice systems to take your leadership skills to the next level.</p>",
